                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37528733/" class="">愚昧作为一种养料</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/56277106/" class=" " title="秋可洛夫斯基">秋可洛夫斯基</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
